{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/AF_Disclaimer_grey.png?t=1736247428\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/maincol_gradient_rule.png?t=1736247428\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/Asgards_Fall_discord_banner.png?t=1736247428\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/maincol_gradient_rule.png?t=1736247428\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/af_boss_615.gif?t=1736247428\" />Embark on an epic saga in <strong>Asgard's Fall</strong>, a norse Survivors-like Roguelite. Fight your way through hordes of creatures and let the gods feel your relentless wrath. How will your saga unfold?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/EN_Headline_Ability_System.png?t=1736247428\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/AF_Skills_30fps_615.gif?t=1736247428\" />Master the art of combat with the dynamic Ability System. Choose from a diverse array of skills, each tailored to your playstyle. Unleash devastating attacks, strategic buffs, and unique powers to conquer the Nine Realms. Forge your warrior's destiny! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/EN_Headline_Rune_Carving.png?t=1736247428\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/AF_Carving_30fps_615.gif?t=1736247428\" />Control the magic of ancient runes with our Rune Carving System. Craft your destiny by engraving powerful runes onto relics, enhancing your power on your way to conquer Asgard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/EN_Headline_Skill_Tree.png?t=1736247428\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/af_skilltree_615.gif?t=1736247428\" />Shape your warrior's evolution with our intricate Skill Tree. Customize your playstyle by unlocking diverse abilities, enhancing strengths, and adapting to challenges. Every choice influences your saga's outcome. Craft a hero uniquely suited to your journey through the nine Realms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484990/extras/AF_Gameplay_615.gif?t=1736247428\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484990/24bf5e80d333ca43dcb89db81c42415bbb2cd7d2.jpg"},{"name":"Berserker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484990/5eb050db39639260d83b7d5da8e380b1e6fe0efd.jpg"},{"name":"Bloodlust","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484990/0496bd460da77eb50ec669d3859d5c4be3ef009b.jpg"},{"name":"Valkyrie's Chosen","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484990/3ce86329f145916499bfc80c7d07c928c92af223.jpg"},{"name":"Odin's Wrath","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484990/b2e87992fe1b11fc367e76d608422d8de32d31bc.jpg"},{"name":"Myth of Midgard","path":"https://cdn.akam